Provides a resource to create a CAM SAML provider.

Example Usage

```hcl
resource "tencentcloud_cam_saml_provider" "example" {
  name        = "tf-example"
  meta_data   = ""
  description = "description."
}
```

Import

CAM SAML provider can be imported using the id, e.g.

```
$ terraform import tencentcloud_cam_saml_provider.example tf-example
```
